---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | Mastercodeon">
    <main class="about-page">
        <h1>About Mastercodeon</h1>
        
        <section class="bio-card">
            <p>
                Hi, I'm <strong>Mastercodeon</strong>. I am a 26-year-old guy whos a self-taught Software Engineer, Ethical Hacker, and Security Researcher with over 13 years of experience diving deep into the world of code, Windows Internals, and offensive security tooling.
            </p>
            <p>
                My core mission is simple: <strong>to build tools that help people and to improve the security of the digital world we live in.</strong> 
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether I am engineering highly optimized data manipulation algorithms, discovering supply chain vulnerabilities, or developing advanced Red Team payloads to simulate real-world adversaries, I am deeply committed to protecting vulnerable individuals and systems from cyber fraud and malicious actors. I thrive on reverse engineering complex systems, automating intricate tasks, and continuously learning on the bleeding edge of cybersecurity.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="skills-section">
            <h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
            <div class="skills-grid">
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3>Languages</h3>
                    <p>C# (Expert), .NET Framework/Core, C, C++, Python, Java, JavaScript, Assembly (x86/x64)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3>Offensive Security</h3>
                    <p>Red Teaming, Payload Development, Evasion (AMSI Patching, API Unhooking), Privilege Escalation (UAC Bypasses), Supply Chain Exploitation</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3>Windows Internals</h3>
                    <p>Extensive Win32 API experience, Memory Management, Process Injection, IFEO Hijacking, WMI, Registry Manipulation</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-card">
                    <h3>Reverse Engineering</h3>
                    <p>dnSpy, Ghidra, IDA Pro, Jadx, Deobfuscation techniques, Malware Analysis</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="collaboration-card">
            <div class="collab-content">
                <h2>Collaborating with Church of Malware</h2>
                <p>
                    I am proud to collaborate with the <strong>Church of Malware</strong>, a nonprofit cybersecurity organization dedicated to advancing security research, education, and threat intelligence. Together, we work to dissect emerging threats, develop defensive tooling, and foster a community committed to securing the digital frontier and protecting users worldwide.
                </p>
                <a href="https://churchofmalware.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="collab-btn">Visit Church of Malware &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .bio-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .bio-card p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #D1D5DB;
  }

  .bio-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .bio-card strong {
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .skills-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .skills-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .skill-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .skill-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .skill-card p {
    color: #9CA3AF;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .collaboration-card {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card-bg) 0%, #000000 100%);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .collaboration-card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .collaboration-card p {
    color: #D1D5DB;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .collab-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--accent-color);
    color: #000000;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .collab-btn:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.6);
    color: #000000;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bio-card, .collaboration-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>